LogicalColumn.name: Company Claim Frequency

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN "%1" = 0 THEN 'A: 0' WHEN "%1" < 5 THEN 'B: < 5' WHEN "%1" < 10 THEN 'C: 5 - 10' WHEN "%1" < 15 THEN 'D: 10 - 15' WHEN "%1" < 20 THEN 'E: 15 - 20' WHEN NOT "%1" IS NULL THEN '>20' END

LogicalColumn.name: Reserve Accuracy %
LogicalColumn.Description: This is accuracy with which the reserve has been estimated and is calculated as the difference between the estimated reserve and the actual claim amount paid as a % of the estimated reserve set aside.

Expr.name: Expr
Expr.ExprText: CASE WHEN ("%1" IS NULL OR "%1" = 0) AND NOT "%2" IS NULL AND "%2" <> 0 THEN 100.0d WHEN ("%1" IS NULL OR "%1" = 0) AND ("%2" IS NULL OR "%2" = 0) THEN 0.0d WHEN "%2" IS NULL AND NOT "%1" IS NULL AND "%1" <> 0 THEN -(100.0d) ELSE 100.0d * ("%2" - "%1") / "%1" END
Expr.ExprTextDesc: CASE WHEN ("Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Reserve Amount" IS NULL OR "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Reserve Amount" = 0) AND NOT "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Paid Amount" IS NULL AND "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Paid Amount" <> 0 THEN 100.0d WHEN ("Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Reserve Amount" IS NULL OR "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Reserve Amount" = 0) AND ("Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Paid Amount" IS NULL OR "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Paid Amount" = 0) THEN 0.0d WHEN "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Paid Amount" IS NULL AND NOT "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Reserve Amount" IS NULL AND "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Reserve Amount" <> 0 THEN -(100.0d) ELSE 100.0d * ("Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Paid Amount" - "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Reserve Amount") / "Core"."Fact - CRM - Ins Claim"."Claim Reserve Amount" END
